verses.verse: Praise <S%H1984><s%> ye <S%H3050>Jehovah<s%>. <S%H1984>Praise<s%> <S%H410>God<s%> in his <S%H6944>sanctuary<s%>: <S%H1984>Praise<s%> him in the <S%H7549>firmament<s%> of his <S%H5797>power<s%>.
Praise <S%H1984><s%> him for his mighty <S%H1369>acts<s%>: <S%H1984>Praise<s%> him according to his <S%H7230>excellent<s%> <S%H1433>greatness<s%>.
Praise <S%H1984><s%> him with <S%H7782>trumpet<s%> <S%H8629>sound<s%>: <S%H1984>Praise<s%> him with <S%H5035>psaltery<s%> and <S%H5035>harp<s%>.
Praise <S%H1984><s%> him with <S%H8596>timbrel<s%> and <S%H4234>dance<s%>: <S%H1984>Praise<s%> him with stringed <S%H4482>instruments<s%> and <S%H5748>pipe<s%>.
Praise <S%H1984><s%> him with <S%H8088>loud<s%> <S%H6767>cymbals<s%>: <S%H1984>Praise<s%> him with high <S%H8643>sounding<s%> <S%H6767>cymbals<s%>.
